{"tid":1306104,"cid":31,"subCid":9,"title":"是噤的，小弟之前整左件衫（岩岩放榜入）","createTime":"2019-07-11T04:42:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-11T09:36:38.000Z","uid":208927,"like":4,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"389f8fd529294ce4c32619a952a02bf7d91a28de","tid":1306104,"uid":208927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T04:42:18.000Z","msg":"利申：<br />\n我明白最近有人食血饅頭，<br />\n但細佬只係想睇下有冇巴打有興趣。<br />\n冇就算，如果睇唔過眼搞到你生氣，<br />\n我道歉先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />歡迎負皮。<br />\n<br />\n細佬當年考完公開試就整左件噤嘅衫<br />\n因為自己想做設計呢味野<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Wubb9m8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWubb9m8.png&h=6e0d48ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qSe9bzW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqSe9bzW.png&h=e7a9bc12&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n前面寫嘅係：<br />\n<br />\n（ DISCLAIMER )<br />\nI<br />\nAUTHORISED<br />\nNO ONE<br />\nTO FUCK UP<br />\nMY LIFE<br />\n<br />\n原意係啲政府機構叫authority<br />\n但當時我唔明我幾撚時有授權比你<br />\n後面個logo就心照啦<br />\n<br />\n有賣過一排幾好賣百幾蚊一件<br />\n但入左U之後就冇理到放左一二邊<br />\n以前就話抽政府水屌下佢幾得意<br />\n賺下呢啲錢都冇所謂<br />\n但宜家屌政府就一啲都唔得意<br />\n我都唔想要賺人呢啲錢<br />\n<br />\n噤岩琴日放榜<br />\n所以我諗有冇岩岩考完試嘅或其他巴絲打想要一件<br />\n鍾意嘅話小弟貼錢低過成本價比你<br />\n唔要都冇所謂的<br />\n<br />\n最後送張台妹圖比大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />要屌屌細力啲<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LKfcTYL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLKfcTYL.png&h=074ecb7e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7f80956184084db56b4041b960796b2d239f5707","tid":1306104,"uid":211989,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T04:46:33.000Z","msg":"老實講<br />\n好柒"},{"pid":"56c8c11a3f4b77bafc5fa3e14fd0202b0819b2fd","tid":1306104,"uid":50658,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T04:46:53.000Z","msg":"負皮係俾樓豬嘅<br />\n食台妹可恥<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2be976f0a7be9bb59d2eceab8c1afb1aacdf66e1","tid":1306104,"uid":208927,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T04:50:31.000Z","msg":"好的細佬明白了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我本身諗住廿蚊連車費<br />\n如果有人鍾意我可以比大家<br />\n唔鍾意就算喇<br />\n對唔住"},{"pid":"d749c02d06987444bf9f3d1593f9140cdf62a3d3","tid":1306104,"uid":44751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2be976f0a7be9bb59d2eceab8c1afb1aacdf66e1","tid":1306104,"uid":208927,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T04:50:31.000Z","msg":"好的細佬明白了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我本身諗住廿蚊連車費<br />\n如果有人鍾意我可以比大家<br />\n唔鍾意就算喇<br />\n對唔住"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T05:00:28.000Z","msg":"又唔好咁 大家都明你心意嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n影埋前面黎睇下<br />\n後面係柒柒地"},{"pid":"2bba089ca102dde78098833f7d3db9f28cd0eafa","tid":1306104,"uid":208927,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d749c02d06987444bf9f3d1593f9140cdf62a3d3","tid":1306104,"uid":44751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2be976f0a7be9bb59d2eceab8c1afb1aacdf66e1","tid":1306104,"uid":208927,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T04:50:31.000Z","msg":"好的細佬明白了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我本身諗住廿蚊連車費<br />\n如果有人鍾意我可以比大家<br />\n唔鍾意就算喇<br />\n對唔住"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T05:00:28.000Z","msg":"又唔好咁 大家都明你心意嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n影埋前面黎睇下<br />\n後面係柒柒地"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T05:05:37.000Z","msg":"唔緊要喇<br />\n我明大家點解負皮<br />\n但係我想講<br />\n考評局個logo真係噤柒嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"371131a55e0863e29691870b9565b281ff8d9566","tid":1306104,"uid":249885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T05:07:37.000Z","msg":"其實ok 吖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/